# Auth-Sentinel

Annotation-driven security framework for Spring Boot 3.x

## Features

- @PublicEndpoint
- @SecuredEndpoint
- @RoleAllowed
- JWT (HS256 / RS256)
- Microservice mode
- SSL Certificate authentication
- Gateway trust mode
- BCrypt password support

## Installation

```xml
<dependency>
  <groupId>io.cosmocoder</groupId>
  <artifactId>cosmo-security-starter</artifactId>
  <version>1.0.0</version>
</dependency>
